1
00:00:00,541 --> 00:00:03,208
This is the entrance they
brought us through, by bus

2
00:00:03,541 --> 00:00:11,958
They brought us down one by
one toward that door and we walked

3
00:00:13,208 --> 00:00:18,875
They lined us up, and our eyes were covered. In the bus
too we were blindfolded, we could not see anything at all

4
00:00:19,750 --> 00:00:24,125
At this door, this entrance
here, we will show it to you

5
00:00:25,333 --> 00:00:29,708
They brought us in through this door one
by one, pressed against the wall like this

6
00:00:29,916 --> 00:00:34,375
They did not bring us in directly,
rather we walked along the wall like this

7
00:00:34,750 --> 00:00:43,625
Along this side we walked one by one next to the wall.
They brought us in through that door, I will show it to you

8
00:00:47,750 --> 00:00:53,291
They brought us in through this door. Of course we
could see people here in <i>shabeh</i> [suspension] and these

9
00:00:53,916 --> 00:01:01,166
Are the devices they used to suspend
people, located in that area like this

10
00:01:01,958 --> 00:01:07,791
Of course we walked through this
corridor, also in a line along the wall

11
00:01:09,958 --> 00:01:21,166
They lined us up. Here there were group cells, and here
there was also a small group cell and a solitary cell

12
00:01:22,291 --> 00:01:27,208
The solitary cells are here, in this area.
The solitary cells I was in are in this spot

13
00:01:30,208 --> 00:01:38,291
This solitary cell, this is where it was. Of course they have now
removed the cinder blocks and taken them apart. Here is a vent

14
00:01:38,541 --> 00:01:45,583
Of course the lights here in this place were on
day and night. We could not tell night from day

15
00:01:46,166 --> 00:01:48,791
Here there is a door. In this place
we could hear them calling the prayer

16
00:01:49,416 --> 00:01:57,500
When they brought food they did not open the door. There is a small
hatch through which they gave us food and then closed it on us

